# рЯІ† 9. Small Mental Model (IMPORTANT)

When writing TypeScript, always think:

рЯСЙ вАЬCan this value change type?вАЭ

* YES вЖТ use `unknown`
* NO вЖТ use strict type (`string`, `number`, etc.)
* NOT SURE вЖТ avoid `any`

