```

---

# рЯІ† 4. Default Parameters

```ts
function greet(name: string, age: number = 18) {
  return `${name} is ${age}`;
}
```

рЯСЙ If no value вЖТ uses default

---

# рЯІ† 5. Function Type (IMPORTANT рЯФ•)

You can define function types separately:

```ts
type AddFunction = (a: number, b: number) => number;

const add: AddFunction = (a, b) => a + b;
```

---

## рЯФ• Why important?

Used in:

* Callbacks
* React props
* APIs

---

# рЯІ† 6. Arrow Functions in TypeScript

```ts
